<p></p>
<p style="Heading 2"><c style="Heading 2" props="font-family:Courier New">Testing </c></p>
<p><c props="font-family:Courier New"><br/></c></p>
<p><c props="font-family:Courier New">To know if if everything worked (or if you´re just curious), you might want to perform a test such as the following: </c></p>
<p><c props="font-family:Courier New"><br/></c></p>
<p><c props="font-family:Courier New">color </c><c props="font-family:Courier New; lang:en-US">colour</c><c props="font-family:Courier New"> </c><c props="font-family:Courier New; lang:de-DE">Farbe</c><c props="font-family:Courier New"> </c></p>
<p><c props="font-family:Courier New"><br/></c></p>
<p><c props="font-family:Courier New">These three words are all marked as being in different languages. This was achieved by double-clicking on each word, opening the Language Dialog, and selecting the intended language. The languages used here are: American English (en-US), British English (en-GB), and German (de-DE). </c></p>
